snippet: The Philadelphia Phillies acquired the seven-time All-Star infielder Michael Young from the Texas Rangers for two relief pitchers, filling a void at third base.
lead_paragraph: The Philadelphia Phillies acquired the seven-time All-Star infielder Michael Young from the Texas Rangers for two relief pitchers, filling a void at third base.
